00:47:25.099 --> 00:47:33.250
Which was a result that so surprised you that
it was like "oh" but you were completely surprised.

00:47:33.250 --> 00:47:35.000
&gt;&gt;Jeremy: Great question.

00:47:35.000 --> 00:47:38.230
The question is which study surprised us the
